snippet.textDisplay:
I'm from Kerala, India and my language is Malayalam. I'm 22 and I'm a fan of coke studio since I started using YouTube.
When I need some relaxation, some meditation I search for coke studio's gems, plug in my headphones 🎧 and close my eyes to enjoy the elegance. Don't even need to understand the lyrics but my eyes and soul will be filled after these minutes. 
I know too many of the people who came here are from different languages and cultures. Love you all. 
Heart felt thanks to coke studio. 
Keep mining Gems ❤️
